## Legacy Codebase Reference

The original Python implementation of Hivemind is located at:

```
/home/ety001/workspace/hivemind_legacy
```

This legacy codebase serves as a reference for:

- API implementation patterns and business logic
- Database schema and queries
- Indexer workflow and block processing
- Steem blockchain interaction patterns

When implementing or debugging features in the Go version, refer to the corresponding Python code in the `hivemind_legacy` directory for guidance on expected behavior and implementation details.

